review:
I would like thank Dr, Sushma specially today when i chat on whatsapp about my wife immediate stomach problem, on only msg...she call us and aks about health and guide us for medicine...am so happy for ur fast service mam..
really its worth consult to u  
thank u soo much once again
She s friendly, caring n empathetic. We had good experience. I recommend this doctor who are seeking treatment
Dr sushma is very friendly. She explained calmly regarding my problem. I have completely recovered from it . I am thankful and greatful to her .
I was suffering from preclamsia during pregnancy she treated me very nicely and she supported me a lot

**** ************** *** has requisite domain expertise .humble and hard working doctor
Patiently listens to the problems and explains with full knowledge and we as patients fully satisfied by the service of the doctor.

My freind suggested me to visit  Dr Sushma.
I had bad obstetric history and looking for experienced obstetrician.  Dr Sushma  took really good care  of me from planning the Prepregnancy till delivery.
She is easily approachable and answered all my phone calls even in odd hours. She provided  excellent care and with her appropriate decision making i finally delivered a healthy child.
I thank Dr sushma and my friend for suggesting me.

Dr sushma is highly professional and very soft spoken she guides appropriately and is very crisp and clear about decision making....many many thank for literally being there with me through entire treatment phase
